    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This can be a double edged sword. While it can do massive damage if many targets are hit, it will most likely attract thier attention which can lead to your immediate demise. Does 597 to 607 damage to any creature caught in the vicinity. 
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
