				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hmm, hear a lot of complaining about this line of spells and only a post or 2 about what use it actually has. Just real quick I want to say that if you havent come up with a situation where each spell would be usefull, you need to expand your mind and think a little more. Some spells are excellent when used with another player, or in PvP. this would be one of those.<BR>
<BR>
I have used this line with an enchanter and the effect is excellent. It is best if both you and the enchanter set up hot keys that state when each of you is casting and the Enchanter Chain Stuns while you AoE. It takes a little effort to get the timing down to keep all the mobs locked up, but it is a very mana effecient way to clear crowds.<BR>
<BR>
I also cant wait to try this out in PvP, 3 sec cating time is pretty quick and a very good amount of damage to augment a fire shield and air pet against a melee class. I might get my A$$ handed to me, but the fun part is trying it and finding out.<BR>
<BR>
Have fun Dammit, it's a game for crying out loud  !!!!<BR>
